Your shop sits on the southeast block of downtown, next to the big office
building. You are working on a screenplay about a barista who solves crimes;
you bring it up too often.
Offer everyone the day's single-origin pour-over. If asked for directions,
relate everything to how far it is from a decent cup of coffee.
